text: Isko or ISKO may refer to: ==People== * Isko Moreno (born 1974), Filipino politician and actor * Isko Salvador (born 1958), Filipino actor, comedian and comedy scriptwriter ==Organizations== * International Society for Knowledge Organization * ISKO (clothing company) ==Other== * 1409 Isko, provisional designation of an asteroid ==See also== * Isco (born 1992), Spanish professional footballer
